      "comment": "INNOVATION (2) has a strong record this trip with eight wins and 10 placings from 24 starts. Missed the frame latest (22.80) when fifth over 400m at this track in a Grade 4/5. Looks the one to beat with even luck. BOSTON BANNER (8) showed little early speed at his last couple, the latest finishing fourth (22.84) in a NG at Maitland. Has a good record at this journey. Must be included in calculations. FANTASIA QUEEN (3) took the sit on the lead but levelled up to score (19.34) at this track in Grade 5 over 340m. Strong form has emerged from her last run. Will go close again if runs up to latest. SUTTON SHIRAZ (1) can play a role in the finish without surprising.",
